{"tid":326222,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"呢場贏唔到既仗應該要點打？","createTime":"2017-07-17T21:50:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-17T23:03:22.000Z","uid":45185,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0c3cd9f2b6a2dfd43c72a7af2d47d7dbacd651bd","tid":326222,"uid":45185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T21:50:03.000Z","msg":"明明已經擁有自己既幸福，<br />\n<br />\n不過人就係咁犯賤走左去參軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n服左幾年兵役贏過幾場勝仗軍階都升到上尉，<br />\n<br />\n然而到最後你發現既係娘娘身邊企左一堆將校級既人物，<br />\n<br />\n雖然娘娘一直安慰住你鼓勵你，但其實你心中有數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一開始就陣亡並唔係一件痛苦既事，<br />\n<br />\n而折磨你既係回憶呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n心酸既係當兵既過程中忽略左好多人既好意<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係好對佢地唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1889e5b925f766a4bb84951bc852ad3c5326efa","tid":326222,"uid":45185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T21:50:31.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cf7dc95f2386a4664c34c06b0405b3acad64b8b","tid":326222,"uid":45185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T21:51:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00eca1a7a1f5b1c9936a9673250317bbb7bc0fbc","tid":326222,"uid":29632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T21:52:27.000Z","msg":"訓啦"},{"pid":"1d9adcc7ac5325366d5421d682622a574a89708e","tid":326222,"uid":45185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T21:53:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>訓啦</blockquote><br />\n你估我唔想瞓咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3de3c258dfbc58d01626bf7296f2bab92c271e06","tid":326222,"uid":29632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T21:54:50.000